        <updateDate>2019-12-02T16:18:40Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Restricting Credit Checks for Employment Decisions Act</b></p> <p>This bill generally prohibits a consumer reporting agency from providing a consumer's credit information for employment purposes, unless otherwise required by law or for a national security investigation. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
